## ğŸ§ª A/B Testing: Finding the Right Balance

### **Test 1: Check-In Frequency**

**Group A:** Weekly goals only  
**Group B:** Weekly + optional daily tips  
**Group C:** Daily goals (Temu style)

**Hypothesis:** Group A will have highest retention, Group C will burn out fastest

### **Test 2: Reward Visibility**

**Group A:** Show progress toward next milestone  
**Group B:** Show all milestones upfront  
**Group C:** Unlock milestones as you go (surprise rewards)

**Hypothesis:** Group A will be most motivating without overwhelming

### **Test 3: Referral Messaging**

**Group A:** â€œBuild your Growth Allianceâ€  
**Group B:** â€œRefer and earn rewardsâ€  
**Group C:** â€œHelp your network save moneyâ€

**Hypothesis:** Group A will get fewer but higher-quality referrals

---

## âœ… The â€œGoldilocks Zoneâ€ Checklist

Before launching any gamification feature, ask:

- [ ] **Does this help them build their business?** (Not just engage with the app)  
- [ ] **Can they ignore it for a week without penalty?** (No streaks, no FOMO)  
- [ ] **Is the reward worth the effort?** (Not 0.03% discounts)  
- [ ] **Would I be annoyed by this?** (Empathy test)  
- [ ] **Does this create long-term value?** (Not just short-term dopamine)

