## ğŸ“Š The Three-Tier Scoring Architecture

```
SITE SCORE (0-1000)
â”œâ”€â”€ Page Quality Score (0-700) [70%]
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Technical SEO (0-200)
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ On-Page SEO (0-300)
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ Content Quality (0-200)
â”‚
â”œâ”€â”€ Community Engagement (0-200) [20%]
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Backlinks Given (0-100)
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Backlinks Received (0-100)
â”‚
â””â”€â”€ Growth Alliance Network (0-100) [10%]
    â”œâ”€â”€ Active Referrals (0-50)
